Package controller

Class SlideShowViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.SlideShowViewController

  • public class SlideShowViewController
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the controller for the slideshow view. The user can go into slideshow view from either album view or the search results view. This view just allows the user to cycle through their photos manually to get a better view of them.
    Author:
    Brian Schillaci
